  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Absorb my power and glory shall be yours”. - The Usurper King</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4f3027dd5a9a148925babe1f18d7a3f3.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=640 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4f3027dd5a9a148925babe1f18d7a3f3.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4f3027dd5a9a148925babe1f18d7a3f3.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield the power of the Usurper as you fight through horrifyingly beautiful planes of existence. Possess your enemies, gain their abilities, and unravel the twisted legacy of a tyrant king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/e1b06bc3a949a3956007fb513baf7e6a.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/e1b06bc3a949a3956007fb513baf7e6a.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/e1b06bc3a949a3956007fb513baf7e6a.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/1b343dd4f3f94ba7920817e5cbc2b131.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/1b343dd4f3f94ba7920817e5cbc2b131.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/1b343dd4f3f94ba7920817e5cbc2b131.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>Challenging Souls-like Combat</strong>:</u> A tough-but-fair Action RPG experience that rewards skill and strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>Unique Possession Mechanic</strong>:</u> Use the Usurping power to possess enemies, turning their abilities against your foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>Local Co-op and Online Play</strong>:</u> Play with friends in local co-op or online using <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong> (instructions below).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <u><strong>Dynamic Environments</strong>:</u> A blend of hand-crafted and procedurally generated dungeons ensures each run feels fresh and exciting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Play with Steam Remote Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/f9a34820db1c31412d9855dce1e47e5e.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=444 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/f9a34820db1c31412d9855dce1e47e5e.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/f9a34820db1c31412d9855dce1e47e5e.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>To play Usurper online with your Steam friends (People you want to play with must be in your steam friend list) follow the instructions below:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Launch the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Make sure your friend is logged in to Steam </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Open your Steam Overlay in-game (shift+tab).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > From your friends list, select 'Remote Play Together'.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your friend will receive an invite. Once your friend accepts the invite, they will be in-game with you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the tale of a King, whose rule was so horrifying, that his soul refused to move on and clinged to the world of the living by possessing the bodies of others by using the power of the Usurper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=436 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
