 friend list) follow the instructions below:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Launch the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Make sure your friend is logged in to Steam </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Open your Steam Overlay in-game (shift+tab).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > From your friends list, select 'Remote Play Together'.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your friend will receive an invite. Once your friend accepts the invite, they will be in-game with you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the tale of a King, whose rule was so horrifying, that his soul refused to move on and clinged to the world of the living by possessing the bodies of others by using the power of the Usurper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.poster.avif?t=1734601690\" width=436 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.webm?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420510/extras/4aa73f16dfb84ac4c83a0a432fb78c40.mp4?t=1734601690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
